<h3>message between client and PeerConnection server</h3>
<dl>
<dt>base protocol</dt>
<dd>HTTP (long-polling model)</dd>
<dt>messages</dt>
<dd>sign_in, wait, sign_out</dd>
<dt>sample body in above messages</dt>
<dd>
  <dl>
  <dt>sign_in</dt>
  <dd>
  <pre class=prettyprint>
komasshu,4,1
my_name,1,1</pre>
  <dt>wait</dt>
  <dd>
  <b>if user 'my_name' disconnected</b>
  <pre class=prettyprint>my_name,1,0</pre>
  <b>if user 'kom' connected</b>
  <pre class=prettyprint>kom,5,1</pre>
  </dd>
  <dt>sign_out</dt>
  <dd></dd>
  </dl>
</dd>
</dl>
